summary:
I decided to redesign momo because her costume is wack and ive seen some others doing at and it seemed fun! 
I gave her a sports...
body:
I decided to redesign momo because her costume is wack and ive seen some others doing at and it seemed fun!

I gave her a sports bra type top for more support and a zipper for emergencies.

The pants are mainly for aesthetic, but also cover a bit more without limiting her quirk.

I made her belt smaller and less bulky with pockets, and changed the book shelf on her back to a smart watch like device on her wrist.

The Cape is for aesthetic and so she can cover up if she needs to.

Finally I gave her high top tennis shoes because they are so much eaiser to run around in than boots and have alot more ankle support.
